. &amp; W. train with Engine No. 68 with two railroad men in front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_122604d992d7deb62cb4716bf32182ea" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_cbd411fa425bad56f807b77d984e21de" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with "Pittston" and L.V.R. on the front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_8f82cac2706ce91bfb57057f0d23f9f3" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_de17f9a4ef4e208f9481f6433f1c7e93" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with four men in front and one in the engine. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_c4e7f2aa7e40c594cbe9c46c9205b90c" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01></dsc>
